Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "nudi" in different forms and positions with their English translations:

1. On *nudi* svoju pomoć svima kojima je potrebna. (He *offers* his help to anyone who needs it.)
2. U restoranu *nude* ukusna jela po pristupačnim cenama. (The restaurant *offers* delicious meals at affordable prices.)
3. Možete li mi *ponuditi* bolju cenu za ovaj proizvod? (Can you *offer* me a better price for this product?)
4. Firma *nudi* mogućnost rada od kuće svim zaposlenima. (The company *offers* the possibility of working from home to all employees.)
5. Oni *ponude* novac kao nagradu za informacije o nestalom psu. (They *offer* money as a reward for information about the missing dog.)
6. Internet prodavnica *nudi* besplatnu dostavu za sve kupovine preko 5000 dinara. (The online store *offers* free delivery for all purchases over 5000 dinars.)
7. Ovaj fakultet *nudi* razne programe studija za buduće studente. (This faculty *offers* various study programs for prospective students.)
8. Nakon dugog putovanja, hotel nam je *ponudio* besplatno osveženje. (After a long journey, the hotel *offered* us a free refreshment.)

Note: I marked the word "nudi" with an asterisk (*) as requested.